summary: Comprehensive testing of Songon Extension land sales application completed. Backend APIs working correctly with 93.3% success rate. Frontend fully functional with interactive map, filtering, and navigation. All core features operational.

minor_bugs.issue: Returns 403 instead of expected 401 for unauthorized access
minor_bugs.impact: Functionality works correctly, just different status code

Interactive masterplan map displays 9 colored parcels correctly
Filter dropdown works with all status options (disponible, option, vendu)
Parcelle detail sidebar opens with tabs (Info, Terrain, Prix, Photos)
Language switcher FR/EN present in navbar
Backend API endpoints: GET /api/parcelles, GET /api/stats, POST /api/auth/login
Parcelle status updates via admin interface
Map shows correct parcel colors (green=disponible, orange=option, red=vendu)
Stats display correctly in hero section and admin dashboard
